Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.46,0:01:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of you guys, we didn't have time to eat anything, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm, this goes down pretty smooth, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.54,0:01:49.58,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an7}The Island Nearest to Paradise\NAugust 11, 2006, 11:00 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.94,0:01:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was thinking there was no other possible way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So was I.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.31,0:02:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,When a person gets caught up in one notion, he becomes unable to think of anything else,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.69,0:02:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,even though, in fact, another way of resolving things is often right before his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.13,0:02:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If we hadn't had that damned campfire,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.68,0:02:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,we might have dragged ourselves right up there and done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.84,0:02:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.96,0:02:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to be grateful to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.56,0:02:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.63,0:02:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good you didn't die, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.37,0:03:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.77,0:03:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.27,0:03:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.88,0:03:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I was more scared than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.10,0:04:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it that at times like this I'm not plagued by lethargy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to just sleep, without thinking about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.16,0:04:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.54,0:05:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.90,0:05:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks like he's from an inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you be the group from the "Island Nearest to Paradise" offline meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.78,0:05:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How does he know about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.02,0:05:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I put a call in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all tired, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.04,0:05:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We can take a hot spring bath and relax a bit before we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.44,0:05:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Jogasaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, now, right this way please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.06,0:05:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we take him up on this offer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.94,0:05:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, come along, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No, I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.18,0:05:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? You're not with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Jogasaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be there as soon as I return the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.05,0:06:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Your names and addresses, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.71,0:06:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:23.19,Note,,0,0,0,,Guest Register
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That was an unbelievable day, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,At this time yesterday, we'd all given up hope about everything in this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and now we're here soaking in a hot spring, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:06:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.87,0:07:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The fools who were going to cast away your lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.71,0:07:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,"Fools," you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Selfishly throwing away the life his parents gave him is something a fool does.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.32,0:07:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you actually were dead now, you'd be beyond all salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.91,0:07:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Things are a little better anyway, since you came back alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.68,0:07:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If you guys hadn't come back safely, what do you think would've happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The marina staff would all have been sent out as search crews.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.60,0:07:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,In the worst case, the people from the fisheries cooperative might have gotten dragged in too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The inns hereabouts would've fallen behind in their work with all the inquiries and whatnot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.68,0:07:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If your bodies had washed up, that would've been big news too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.04,0:07:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Worst case, if they'd drifted up near the inns, it'd have an impact on the lodge businesses here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.78,0:08:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be huge trouble all around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.45,0:08:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Now do you see the idiocy of fools who would throw away their lives and cause trouble to others
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.90,0:08:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,just because of their own situations?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.69,0:08:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do understand, then don't ever think up anything so stupid again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.04,0:08:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a warning from somebody who was a fool himself long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.01,0:08:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hana-Hana's running late, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.81,0:08:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Women's baths take a long time, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.42,0:08:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing for it. Shall we start without her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.21,0:08:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I'm sure that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.49,0:08:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.26,0:08:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I had that young man Jogasaki go get it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You were out for a drive?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a bit. It's such a nice car, I couldn't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.08,0:09:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Women really are tougher than men.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.54,0:09:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Nomura, Mr. Kusano, members of your family are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hidehito!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about the clinic!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.53,0:09:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave it to your father!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.83,0:09:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All this because you can't become a doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.22,0:09:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.95,0:09:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:10:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you do something so stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The fault is all mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no excuse for what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.18,0:10:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And you! Dragging our son into this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.93,0:10:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.08,0:10:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.48,0:10:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because I'm such a wimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.64,0:10:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,To have my mother cry at me like that is too much. I got worn out and escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.51,0:10:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming from me, it doesn't mean much, but it is wrong to want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.69,0:11:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,After all this, I talked to my mother for the first time in a long time, and I finally understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.19,0:11:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as there's someone who'll grieve, it's wrong to want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.47,0:11:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato, this is for you, if you're interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.09,0:11:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a free pass to "Ultimate Fantasy," an online game.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.68,0:11:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If you type in this number, you can play for the first month for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.48,0:11:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a hikikomori, right, Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.63,0:11:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A person I met online is also a hikikomori, and he's making a ton of money off of this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.87,0:11:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Off of a game?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.45,0:11:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He does R.M.T.: "Real Money Trading."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.62,0:11:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He trades items and gold he acquires in the game for real money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.09,0:11:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, even if you're shut inside your house, you can earn money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.69,0:12:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's perfect for you, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"Vina Teelo"...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.22,0:12:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, I'll give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.93,0:12:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,See you in Vina Teelo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.24,0:12:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you can't die at least until you meet him inside the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.54,0:12:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hidehito! Hidehito!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to head out too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.95,0:12:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We probably won't meet again, but take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.19,0:12:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hidehito, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm over here. Don't yell like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're back, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.35,0:13:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get going soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, are...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.07,0:13:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki and the...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.74,0:13:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki said he had something important to do;
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.69,0:13:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,he left a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.67,0:13:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Something important to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:30.70,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&HF56C72&\frz44.896\pos(296.629,231.429)}Sample!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.71,0:13:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you charge 3,000 yen for a trial version?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he crazy or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.38,0:13:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So, he's saying the Comic Stall is more important than I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.49,0:13:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And about that girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.58,0:13:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.28,0:13:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,She just vanished at some point; I think she probably went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't really concerned about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:13:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you ride back in my car?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm in the mood to go home by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.90,0:14:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, once things settle down, let's get together in Tokyo to eat or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.53,0:14:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Hitomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.73,0:14:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm truly sorry I got you caught up in this kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.76,0:14:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish you happiness, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.23,0:15:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a ride to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.84,0:15:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Makoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.79,0:15:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.85,0:15:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.40,0:15:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom told me to come meet you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She said let's all give it another try.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:34.84,Note,,0,0,0,,Misaki Nakahara
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.81,0:16:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a hikikomori, more pathetic than a stray dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...so much more of a throwaway hunk of refuse than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So... You can't die! Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.39,0:17:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get her at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.51,0:17:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alive, Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.63,0:17:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it, I didn't think the Comic Stall customers would all be jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.25,0:17:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Learn to read things' auras!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.28,0:17:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't they even realize that once it's completed it's going to be a big-name item?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.63,0:17:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What hurt us is that we didn't get to go on the first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.27,0:17:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Games weren't the main items today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.90,0:17:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.87,0:17:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care how much you despaired about your hikikomori life;
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:18:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,there was no reason to stir up so much crap on the day of Comic Stall!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The idiots in my class are giving me cold glares too; I've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:12.57,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an2\c&H011B34&\bord0\shad0\fnSegoe Script\move(763.334,367.5,346.666,367.5,0,4466)\frz18.966}I'll be waiting at the usual place, at the usual time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting at the usual place, at the usual time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:15.07,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an2\bord0\shad0\fnSegoe Script\fscx360\fscy276.25\move(763.334,574.79,650,574.79,8,2469)\frz9.868\c&H2E455A&}I'll be waiting
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.94,0:18:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.34,0:18:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you come with me to see the fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.34,0:18:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I think positive things would come out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.91,0:18:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're together, I'm sure you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.69,0:18:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! If it were at least finished,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.61,0:18:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,those idiots would understand at least a little how wonderful our game is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.69,0:18:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.19,0:19:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a copy of the contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.24,0:19:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,These past few days, you skipped counseling without permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.64,0:19:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a complete violation of this contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.04,0:19:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'll be collecting that fine of one million yen."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You were...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is what I could say.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.98,0:19:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was also keeping my house a secret from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.23,0:19:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel a little guilty about that. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.91,0:19:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result, I'll dispense with the fine this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.16,0:19:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting tomorrow, we'll do counseling as we did previously,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.86,0:20:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but you absolutely must come.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.83,0:20:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you to decide things for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.18,0:20:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you came back for me, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.60,0:20:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.32,0:20:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad to be home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.66,0:20:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.39,0:21:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.93,0:21:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Tatsuhiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.31,0:21:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Mom, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to talk to you a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's sure a gloomy voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she heard something about the offline meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.85,0:21:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the gloomy voice? That's not like you, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.65,0:21:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm feeling really well on my end.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.58,0:21:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.02,0:21:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? So, it's not about the offline meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuhiro? Stay calm and listen, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.25,0:21:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, I'm sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.57,0:21:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I can't hear you very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.28,0:21:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.48,0:21:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:22:00.00,Note,,0,0,0,,{\c&H72AA7B&\fs60.504\pos(640,136.135)}Episode 14
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:22:00.00,Note,,0,0,0,,{\c&H45894E&\pos(656.18,468.907)\fs60.504}Welcome to Reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.88,0:21:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're joking, right, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.22,0:23:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You gather companions and adventure together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.42,0:23:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You work too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.61,0:23:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe this to you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.38,0:23:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode, "Welcome to the Fantasy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.38,0:23:40.00,Note,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFB94C&\pos(640,113.445)\fs60.504}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.38,0:23:40.00,Note,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFEA30C&\pos(640,446.219)\fs60.504}Welcome to the Fantasy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.01,0:00:16.18,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,I lift my eyes a little and look into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.34,0:00:19.26,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,All I do is mutter every time,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.33,0:00:22.31,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,as I turn my back
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.31,0:00:24.64,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,on this perfect everyday life
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.64,0:00:27.81,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,"Where am I supposed to go?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.98,0:00:32.86,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,With you who are giving me a look like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.28,0:00:42.20,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,In the shadows of a back alley,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.12,0:00:49.33,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,the hands of a clock repaint the time that has been stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:53.07,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,Extended hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.19,0:00:57.44,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,puzzle pieces that don't fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:01:01.74,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,Until the abandoned two
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.74,0:01:05.79,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,reunite with something
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:10.42,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,that has been lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.42,0:01:13.96,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,Recover
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:18.22,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,the last piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.09,0:01:24.35,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,and let's start walking.
